Package com.main_system

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddQuestionPage
    This class represents the "Add Question" page for the admin to add new questions to the quiz system.
    AdminHomePage
    AdminHomePage class that represents the home page of the admin interface.
    AllPlayers
    JFrame to display all players with their short details and show full details for a specific player.
    Competitor
    Represents a competitor in the system.
    DeleteQuestionPage
    JFrame for deleting a question from the database.
    Main
    The Main class contains the entry point of the application and initiates the login page and console menu.
    Name
    The Name class represents a person's full name and provides methods to retrieve the full name, initials, and set/get individual name components (first name, middle name, last name).
    PlayQuiz
    This class represents the Play Quiz page where a competitor can play a quiz with multiple rounds.
    Question
    Represents a question in the quiz.
    QuizReportManager
    Manages the generation of quiz reports and statistics.
    RegisterPage
    Represents the registration page for the SmartQuizHub application.
    ShowQuestionsPage
    Represents the page where quiz questions are displayed based on the selected level.
    UpdateQuestionPage
    This class represents the page for updating a quiz question in the system.
    ViewReportsPage
    This class represents the View Reports page where administrators can view quiz results.
